              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Biden blocks Nippon Steel’s US Steel deal</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/ls-jan-6-1.jpg" alt="Biden blocks Nippon Steel’s US Steel deal" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">President Biden has <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-06-01-2025-h1-1-halted" target="_blank">halted</a> Nippon Steel’s $14.1 billion acquisition of US Steel, citing national security risks. The U.S. views domestic steel production as vital for national security and wants US-controlled steelmaking to safeguard supply chains and defense infrastructure. US Steel’s <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-06-01-2025-h1-2-stock-fell" target="_blank">stock fell</a> by 6.5% following the announcement. The blockage sparked diplomatic tensions between Japan and the U.S., with trade officials demanding an explanation. Nippon and US Steel plan to challenge the decision legally, calling it politically motivated.</p>
        </mj-text>
